@host = http://localhost:4004/api
@authToken = {{login.response.body.accessToken}}

### Admit Patient
POST {{host}}/admissions/admit
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

{
  "patientId": "{{patientId}}",
  "wardId": "{{wardId}}",
  "admissionDate": "2024-01-01T12:00:00",
  "reason": "Surgery recovery"
}

### Discharge Patient
PUT {{host}}/admissions/discharge/{{admissionId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### Get Active Admissions (CQRS Read Model)
GET {{host}}/admissions/active
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
